targets.query: SELECT "cpu_time", "duration", "logical_reads"*8, "physical_reads"*8, row_count, "writes", "session_id", "AxSession", "AxUser", "SqlEventName", "SqlHostName", "SqlUser", "SqlQueryHash","hex_query_hash", "queryplan_hash","hex_queryplan_hash", "DatabaseName", "result","isFetch" FROM "queryhashcodemetrics"."sqlXeEvents" WHERE "SqlQueryHash" =~ /^$QueryHash$/ AND "AxUser" =~ /^$USER$/ AND "SqlUser" =~ /^$SQLUSER$/ AND "SqlEventName" =~ /^$sqleventname$/ AND "SqlHostName" =~ /^$CLIENTHOST$/ AND "AxSession" =~ /^$SESSION$/ AND  "SQLInstance" =~ /^$SQLINSTANCE$/ AND $timeFilter

SELECT "duration", "cpu_time", "logical_reads"*8, "physical_reads"*8, "writes", "row_count", "session_id", "cursor_id", "AxUser", "AxSession", "SqlHostName","SqlUser","query_hash", "query_hash_hex", "query_plan_hash", "query_plan_hash_hex" FROM "queryhashcodemetrics"."sqlXeFetches" WHERE ("AxUser" =~ /^$USER$/ AND "query_hash" =~ /^$FetchesQueryHash$/ AND "AxSession" =~ /^$SESSION$/ AND "SQLInstance" =~ /^$SQLINSTANCE$/ AND "SqlHostName" =~ /^$CLIENTHOST$/ AND "SqlUser" =~ /^$SQLUSER$/) AND $timeFilter

SELECT "duration", "session_id", "cursor_id", "AxUser", "AxSession", "query_hash", "query_hash_hex", "query_plan_hash", "query_plan_hash_hex", "cpu_time", "logical_reads", "physical_reads", "writes", "row_count" FROM "queryhashcodemetrics"."sqlXeFetches" WHERE ("AxUser" =~ /^$USER$/ AND "query_hash" =~ /^$FetchesQueryHash$/ AND "AxSession" =~ /^$SESSION$/ AND "SQLInstance" =~ /^$SQLINSTANCE$/ AND "SqlHostName" =~ /^$CLIENTHOST$/ AND "SqlUser" =~ /^$SQLUSER$/) AND $timeFilter

list.name: SQLNODE
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "host"

list.name: SQLINSTANCE
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "SQLInstance"  where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/

list.name: USER
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "AxUser" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/

list.name: SQLUSER
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "SqlUser" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/

list.name: SESSION
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "AxSession" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/

list.name: CLIENTHOST
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "SqlHostName" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/

list.name: DBNAME
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "DatabaseName" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/

list.label: QUERYHASH
list.name: QueryHash
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeEvents" WITH KEY = "SqlQueryHash" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/

list.label: FETCHES QUERYHASH
list.name: FetchesQueryHash
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "sqlXeFetches" WITH KEY = "query_hash" where "host" =~ /^$SQLNODE$/ and "SQLInstance" =~/^$SQLINSTANCE$/
